  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">In triangle <math alttext=\"upper D upper E upper F\"><mrow>\n\t<mi>D</mi>\n\t<mi>E</mi>\n\t<mi>F</mi>\n</mrow>\n</math>, the measure of angle <math alttext=\"upper D\"><mi>D</mi>\n</math> is <math alttext=\"47 degree\"><mrow><mn>47</mn></mrow><mo>&#176;</mo></math> and the measure of angle <math alttext=\"upper E\"><mi>E</mi>\n</math> is <math alttext=\"97 degree\"><mrow><mn>97</mn></mrow><mo>&#176;</mo></math>. In triangle <math alttext=\"upper R upper S upper T\"><mrow>\n\t<mi>R</mi>\n\t<mi>S</mi>\n\t<mi>T</mi>\n</mrow>\n</math>, the measure of angle <math alttext=\"upper R\"><mi>R</mi>\n</math> is <math alttext=\"47 degree\"><mrow><mn>47</mn></mrow><mo>&#176;</mo></math> and the measure of angle <math alttext=\"upper S\"><mi>S</mi>\n</math> is <math alttext=\"97 degree\"><mrow><mn>97</mn></mrow><mo>&#176;</mo></math>. Which of the following additional pieces of information is needed to determine whether triangle <math alttext=\"upper D upper E upper F\"><mrow>\n\t<mi>D</mi>\n\t<mi>E</mi>\n\t<mi>F</mi>\n</mrow>\n</math> is similar to triangle <math alttext=\"upper R upper S upper T\"><mrow>\n\t<mi>R</mi>\n\t<mi>S</mi>\n\t<mi>T</mi>\n</mrow>\n</math>?</p>",
